1. *Radeći* ovaj projekat, shvatila sam koliko sam sposobna. (Working on this project, I realized how capable I am.)
2. Da bismo stigli na vreme, moramo *radeći* put da pređemo 500 kilometara. (To arrive on time, we have to travel 500 kilometers, working our way through.)
3. *Radeći* svoj posao sa strašću, ona je postigla veliki uspeh u karijeri. (Working her job with passion, she achieved great success in her career.)
4. Čitajući knjigu, primetio sam da *radeći* karakter glavnog junaka ima dosta sličnosti sa mojim. (Reading the book, I noticed that the character of the main protagonist, while working, has a lot of similarities with mine.)
5. Oni su ostvarili mnogo *radeći* zajedno kao tim. (They have achieved a lot, working together as a team.)
6. *Radeći* na svom fakultetskom radu, studenti su morali da se suoče sa mnogim izazovima. (Working on their university paper, students had to face many challenges.)
7. *Radeći* vežbe, on je naučio kako da prevaziđe svoje strahove i fobije. (Working out, he learned how to overcome his fears and phobias.)
8. Kada budeš *radeći* na svom samopouzdanju, primetićeš veliku promenu u svom životu. (When you start working on your self-confidence, you will notice a big change in your life.)
9. *Radeći* na ovom projektu, imao sam priliku da naučim mnoge nove stvari. (Working on this project, I had the opportunity to learn many new things.)
10. Njihova kompanija je postala uspešna zahvaljujući svim zaposlenima koji su *radeći* dali svoj maksimum. (Their company has become successful thanks to all employees who, by working, gave their best.)